ISLAMABAD, Feb 24 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain on Monday said the ongoing visit of Prime Minister Imran Khan to Russia was taking place as per the schedule and all the speculations in this regard were misleading.
“Speculations about PM Imran Khan visit are misplaced. The visit is proceeding and PM will return Pakistan tonight as per schedule,” he tweeted.
